@startuml
' @id(SEQ-MAP-STATUS)
' @ref(USE-MAP-FRESHNESS)
' @desc(SEQ-MAP-STATUS, "Implemented as Project::map_status (crates/mdd-core/src/lib.rs), invoked by mdd-cli Commands::MapStatus. read_map_source_revision reads .mdd/map/manifest.yml source_revision; None -> MapStatusReport { fresh: true, source_revision: None }. Otherwise traceability::changed_code(root, source_revision) is intersected with trace.yml source_links (path + symbol_matches) to build the drift list of MapDrift { path, symbol, model_id }; fresh = drift.is_empty(). The CLI prints FRESH/STALE and exits 0/1.")
' Current-side sequence for the freshness check (cycle 0013), as built.
title mdd map-status freshness (current)

actor "Developer / Agent" as Dev
participant "mdd map-status\n(Commands::MapStatus)" as Cli
participant "Project::map_status" as Status
participant "read_map_source_revision\n(.mdd/map/manifest.yml)" as Manifest
participant "traceability::changed_code\n(git + syn)" as Engine
participant "trace.yml\nsource_links" as Trace

Dev -> Cli : mdd map-status
Cli -> Status : map_status()
Status -> Manifest : source_revision?
alt none
  Manifest --> Status : None
  Status --> Cli : MapStatusReport { fresh, no baseline }
else present
  Manifest --> Status : source_revision
  Status -> Engine : changed_code(root, source_revision)
  Engine --> Status : ChangedCode { symbols, glue }
  Status -> Trace : changed symbols covered by a source_link?
  Trace --> Status : tracked drift set
  Status --> Cli : fresh = drift.is_empty(); drift list
end
Cli --> Dev : FRESH / STALE + drift (exit 0 / 1)
@enduml
